body:
## Steps to reproduce the issue

`./yosys -p "proc" xsignext.v -b verilog`

```
module top(input clk, output [32:0] o);
assign o = 'bx;
endmodule
```

## Expected behavior

```
(* cells_not_processed =  1  *)
(* src = "xsignext.v:1" *)
module top(clk, o);
  (* src = "xsignext.v:1" *)
  input clk;
  (* src = "xsignext.v:1" *)
  output [32:0] o;
  assign o = 33'hxxxxxxxxx;
endmodule
```

## Actual behavior

```
(* cells_not_processed =  1  *)
(* src = "xsignext.v:1" *)
module top(clk, o);
  (* src = "xsignext.v:1" *)
  input clk;
  (* src = "xsignext.v:1" *)
  output [32:0] o;
  assign o = 33'h0xxxxxxxx;
endmodule
```

Extracted from https://github.com/cliffordwolf/picorv32/blob/e0baf2e0bd49fdddef2e3440c1f6364478655154/picorv32.v#L1444

